Package: iFraudSimulator
Type: Package
Title: Package to generate insurance fraud network data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Bavo D.C. Campo
Maintainer: Bavo D.C. Campo <bavo.campo@kuleuven.be>
Description: This package contains the code to run the simulation engine as described in Campo, B.D.C, and Antonio, K. (2023) <arXiv:2308.11659>. The engine creates a synthetic data set with a similar network structure and available covariates as the one used in Óskarsdóttir et al. (2022). <doi:10.1111/risa.13693>.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0), data.table, doParallel, ggplot2, Matrix, doSNOW
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown, PRROC, lift, bookdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Imports: Hmisc, htmlTable, igraph, randomNames, gridExtra, copula, magrittr, lubridate, plyr, methods, foreach
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
